msgid "Display"
msgstr "显示屏"

#: ../../source/hardware/display.rst:8 cc8ee3e28a7540b0bf15bcf2fdedb5d3
msgid "A lcd display library"
msgstr "LCD 屏幕显示库"

#: ../../source/hardware/display.rst:15 d7d78471f8d34c67b18fa0b9227f709c
msgid "M5 Series Display Libraries"
msgstr "M5 系列显示库说明"

#: ../../source/hardware/display.rst:18 f5eb7fd716aa49efbebe1969e5076562
msgid "1. Display"
msgstr "1. 显示"

#: ../../source/hardware/display.rst:19 64f796c2147d4a5da8876c04a54fe8b2
msgid ""
"A low-level graphics library providing basic screen drawing, text, lines,"
" and color management."
msgstr "底层图形库，提供屏幕绘制、文字、线条、颜色管理等基础功能。"

#: ../../source/hardware/display.rst:20 dcad8a26c61742e18aab1c436cfddee0
msgid ""
"Can be used independently, suitable for scenarios that only require "
"drawing graphics or text."
msgstr "可独立使用，适合只需要绘制图形或文字的场景。"

#: ../../source/hardware/display.rst:23 19332ca94ea14bc7af7fbf970ee6941f
msgid "2. M5Widgets"
msgstr "2. M5Widgets"

#: ../../source/hardware/display.rst:24 23cea27464254c23b17685a7f8a43a41
msgid ""
"A basic UI widget library providing labels, image displays, and other UI "
"controls."
msgstr "基础控件库，提供标签、图片显示等 UI 控件。"

#: ../../source/hardware/display.rst:25 2ca8da12a33947b6ace23e2a60c9400a
msgid "Built on top of M5GFX."
msgstr "底层依赖 M5GFX。"

#: ../../source/hardware/display.rst:26 bc1cd21c333947b3b5bd2edef48041ab
msgid "Suitable for simple interactive UI elements."
msgstr "适合需要简单交互控件的界面。"

#: ../../source/hardware/display.rst:29 0bf7ed421b2f4ca99c5e3ccb9c0de4ad
msgid "3. M5UI"
msgstr "3. M5UI"

#: ../../source/hardware/display.rst:30 c6a68fc1ad224fd7ab6a9d668271accf
msgid "A high-level UI framework based on LVGL."
msgstr "高层 UI 框架，基于 LVGL 封装。"

#: ../../source/hardware/display.rst:31 ed5ea04f7b3248099da440c7d1a5f344
msgid ""
"Provides page management, multi-widget layouts, and unified event "
"handling."
msgstr "提供页面管理、多控件布局和统一事件处理。"

#: ../../source/hardware/display.rst:34 20f08550e7c04b7f9c5b9d54aa04b67e
msgid "Usage Tips"
msgstr "使用提示"

#: ../../source/hardware/display.rst:35 e15526db1dba4c8da488cad7065e1594
msgid ""
"⚠️ Do not mix M5GFX, M5Widgets, and M5UI simultaneously, as it may cause "
"rendering issues or event conflicts."
msgstr "⚠️ 不建议同时混用 M5GFX、M5Widgets、M5UI，可能导致渲染异常或事件冲突。"

#: ../../source/hardware/display.rst:36 f18a4752adee45af976947e640c53882
msgid "For graphics-only drawing → use M5GFX."
msgstr "单独绘图 → 使用 M5GFX。"

#: ../../source/hardware/display.rst:37 b26ba8ef9aa24951a2ad020a51d89623
msgid "For simple interactive widgets → use M5Widgets."
msgstr "简单控件交互 → 使用 M5Widgets。"

#: ../../source/hardware/display.rst:38 5c6440a3007f4418afd152d2019c902c
msgid "For multi-page UI → use M5UI."
msgstr "多页面 UI → 使用 M5UI。"

